'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #3299] on 06 July 2001'!"Change Set:		tinyMenu-je77Date:			6 July 2001Author:			Je77 RickProvides an improved menu icon for System Windows(Tweaked by sw)"!!SystemWindow methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'je77 & sw 07/2001'!addMenuControl"If I have a label area, add a menu control to it. "	| frame |	labelArea ifNil: [^ self].  "No menu if no label area"	menuBox _ IconicButton new borderWidth: 0;			labelGraphic: (ScriptingSystem formAtKey: 'TinyMenu'); color: Color transparent; 			actWhen: #buttonDown;			actionSelector: #offerWindowMenu; target: self;			setBalloonText: 'window menu'.	frame _ LayoutFrame new.	frame leftFraction: 0; leftOffset: 17; topFraction: 0; topOffset: 1.	menuBox layoutFrame: frame.	labelArea addMorph: menuBox! !"Postscript:Replace the icon for TinyMenu"ScriptingSystem saveForm: ((ColorForm	extent: 12@9	depth: 1	fromArray: #( 0 2145386496 2145386496 1616904192 1616904192 1616904192 2145386496 2145386496 0)	offset: 0@0)	colorsFromArray: #(#(0.0 0.0 0.0) #( )  )) atKey: 'TinyMenu'.!